caption.text:
Ori and the blind forest:
Septiembre ha sido un mes de muchos lanzamientos excelentes pero no debes dejar pasar este increíble video juego cortesia de Microsoft,con un nivel artístico pocas veces visto que me recuerda un poco al diseño de los últimos Rayman, pero mejorado x10. El ritmo de juego es rápido, innovador, los movimientos de Ori son fluidos , veloces , llenos de acción desde el ataque, equivar , hasta algo tan sencillo como saltar y trepar. Cuando mueres puedes volver rápidamente al lugar donde tuviste dificultades y en ningún momento se vuelve tedioso repetir algunas situaciones, a diferencia de algunos juegos que el movimiento lento del personaje puede llegar a hartar si te ves en una situación que necesite mayor tiempo.
La música es genial , se acopla perfectamente a la ambientación de los escenarios, el tema principal es de lo más melancólico que he escuchado para un video juego y puede sonar en tu cabeza días.
Un metroidvania que para mi, pese a ser un juego del año 2016, permanece totalmente fresco y dio más impulso( junto a otros títulos ) a este género que tiene casi 30 años.
Muy recomendado.

Gameplay luchando si no mal recuerdo con el primer mini boss.

The Contra Anniversary Collection is the third of Konami’s releases in celebration of the company’s 50th birthday. Prior to the release of this collection they also put out an Arcade Classics Collection and the Castlevania Collection. This package has been developed in conjunction with M2, so you know from the get-go that this is going to be a perfectly polished collection which respects the originals!⠀
⠀
The game was then announced as a shadow drop during the 2019 E3 Nintendo Direct presentation. A brilliant moment for Contra fans where Konami announced the collection would be released following the presentation and also announced a new game in the series, Contra Rogue Corps, to be released in September.⠀

THE LAST OF US 2 ENTRA EM PRÉ-VENDA NO BRASIL E CONFIRMA DATA DE LANÇAMENTO

Uma das maiores surpresas para os donos de PlayStation 4 nesta semana foi o anúncio de que The Last of Us Part II será lançado em fevereiro do próximo ano. Para aqueles que estão contando os dias para colocar as mãos no jogo, a Sony já iniciou o período de reserva do título.

Ao visitar a página oficial da Sony Store o jogador tem a chance de comprar o game por R$ 199,90. Somado a isso, também foi confirmada a data de lançamento do próximo título da série por aqui para 21 de fevereiro.

Quem comprar o game antecipadamente vai receber o avatar Tattoo, além de upgrade de capacidade de munição para a pistola e o manual de treinamento para criação de itens.

The Last of Us Part II é um game exclusivo para PlayStation 4.

Electronic Arts ha ufficialmente rilasciato EA SPORTS FIFA 20 su PlayStation 4, Xbox One e PC.

Con il lancio della scorsa settimana per EA Access e Origin Access, i giocatori di tutto il mondo hanno già iniziato a formare le loro squadre dei sogni e a scontrarsi sul campo, con oltre 57 milioni di partite totali giocate, più di 3 milioni di squadre create e più di 52 milioni di gol segnati durante i match.

Più di 30 campionati ufficiali, 700 squadre, 17.000 giocatori e 90 stadi con licenza di tutto il mondo danno vita a uno dei videogiochi sportivi più realistici di sempre. Tantissime le licenze disponibili, incluse le più grandi competizioni mondiali, dai massimi livelli del calcio di club con la UEFA Champions League al mondo dei fan senza rivali della Bundesliga, della Premier League, della LaLiga Santander e molte altre.

Echoes 
Thank you for all the likes on the Smash Bros. drawings I've posted throughout this month. As previously mentioned it took me a while to get through all of them, especially the last  two, but regardless I'm glad I finally got around to sharing the series on here.  If you're a fan of the game you probably realized that I didn't have a drawing for the DLC fighters, the reason for that is simply I wanted to wait until they were all revealed (knowing full well that it would most likely be a year later until that happens😅😓). Nevertheless here we are a year later and 4 outta 5 characters have been revealed, I'm hoping the 5th is announced soon. That being said I don't have any intentions on doing the full 31 day Inktober challenge but instead will draw the DLC fighters. October for some reason always ends up being a really busy month for me so let's see how this goes 😂

caption.text: Here is #tacticianmagician themselves, the #robins. I kinda wanted to roll with the #mordernizing #idea with the Robins #casualoutfits. For #malerobin I turned his #famous robe into a #jacket, and he's wearing a shirt that says his famous line "Time to tip the scales" with his Levendsword on it. For #femalerobin I based her #casuallook off of male Robin, instead of purple sleeves on her jacket, she has purple stripes, and shes has triangles at the bottom of her jacket similar to the original robe. And instead of jeans, she wears shorts, she's also wearing a shirt that says "Best mom" in #reference to female Robin being #lucinas mother. I hope you guys like the #drawing.

title: Brain Age: Nintendo Switch Training announced for Switch

caption.text:
.
.
Nintendo has announced Brain Age: Nintendo Switch Training for Switch. It will launch on December 27 in Japan for 3,480 yen at retail and include an official Switch stylus accessory, or 2,680 yen via download. The stylus will also be sold separately for 864 yen. A western release was not announced.
.
Brain Age: Nintendo Switch Training is the latest entry in the puzzle game series that began on DS in 2005. In addition to the standard exercises featured in the series thus far, there are also exercises that utilize the IR motion camera to read your hand motions, as well as two-player competitive exercises. New elements such as an alarm to schedule training, e-mail summaries, online leaderboards, and world tournaments have also been added.
.
It should be noted that five total exercises that require the Joy-Con are not playable on Switch Lite, and that the game is not compatible with paired Joy-Cons, the Joy-Con grip, or the Switch Pro Controller. It is only playable with the Joy-Con sideways.
.

Blapshemous è un action in 2D con un ambientazione decisamente sopra le righe ricca di nemici ed equipaggiamenti unici.

Una terribile maledizione si è abbattuta sulla terra di Cvstodia e sui suoi abitanti – è conosciuta come Il Miracolo.

Gioca nei panni del Penitente, unico sopravvissuto al massacro del “Dolore Silenzioso”. Intrappolato in un ciclo infinito di morte e rinascita, spetta a te liberare il mondo da questo terribile destino e raggiungere l’origine del tuo tormento.

Esplora questo angosciante mondo di religioni contorte e scopri i suoi numerosi segreti nascosti nel profondo. Usa combo devastanti ed esecuzioni brutali per colpire orde di mostri grotteschi e boss titanici pronti a farti a pezzi. Trova ed equipaggia reliquie, rosari e preghiere che invocano i poteri dei cieli per aiutarti a compiere la tua missione e rompere la tua dannazione eterna.
